dTunes Music Bot - Privacy Policy
Effective Date: [10/01/2025]

This Privacy Policy explains how dTunes collects, uses, and protects your information when you use the dTunes Music Bot ("Bot"). By using the Bot, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in this policy.

1. Information We Collect:

dTunes collects the following types of information:

User Information: When you interact with the Bot, we may collect your Discord username and user ID.
Interaction Data: We collect information about your interactions with the Bot, including music requests, commands issued, and server activity.
Server Information: We collect basic server data, such as server name and ID, to provide proper functioning of the Bot in your Discord server.

2. How We Use Your Information:

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

To provide and improve the functionality of the Bot.
To monitor and enhance the user experience.
To comply with applicable laws and regulations.
To prevent abuse or misuse of the Bot.

3. Data Retention:

We retain user interaction data and server information for the duration of your use of the Bot. If you stop using the Bot, your data may be removed or anonymized after a reasonable period.

4. Sharing Your Information
dTunes does not sell, trade, or rent your personal data to third parties. However, we may share data with trusted third-party service providers who assist in operating the Bot, maintaining servers, or analyzing data, provided they comply with our privacy practices.

5. Data Security:

We take reasonable precautions to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, we cannot guarantee the complete security of your data and disclaim any responsibility for data breaches or security incidents.

6. Third-Party Links:

The Bot may provide links to third-party websites or services, including music streaming platforms. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party services.

7. User Rights:

You have the right to:

Request access to the personal information we hold about you.
Request correction or deletion of your data.
Opt-out of certain data collection practices if applicable.
To exercise these rights, contact us directly at [Insert Contact Info].

8. Changes to Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. You will be notified of significant changes, and by continuing to use the Bot, you accept the updated policy.

9. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at our discord support server [" https://discord.gg/CpWzhacSYv "].

